{"type":null,"faqId":32785,"title":"为什么在灯光下拍摄视频的时候会出现水波纹？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">手机摄像时出现水波纹是因为灯光由交流电供电，具有一定的闪烁频率，如果灯光频率与摄像头扫描频率不匹配时会出现水波纹现象，因为不同国家和地区的市电频率不同，为了实现兼容，在拍摄视频时需要实时识别电频率，就会出现水波纹。这时如果距离灯源比较近或拍摄视频过程中变换场景，有时就会出现水波纹。属于正常现象。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7487","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748406000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":17,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"灯光,视频,录像,水波纹","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}